_sText:
Okey here we are with a new version of this aim map! The new map includes: Fixed position of all the grenades, possible way to get LOADS of more weapons (in hidden places), New hidden areas, death traps, som "face-lifting" on the designe like new static objects, All the ugly boxes are fixed with new slimed textures. We have also fixed th gameplay of this map, by moving the awp:s to a more difficult area to enter. That made the awp less power. We have also added more spawn points, more weapons in the spawn area,  5 new teleports. 

List of weapons avaible:

*M4A1
*Famas
*AK-47
*GALIL

*M249

We hope you enjoy!
